=== 1.0.3 / 2012-04-13

* bug fixes for 1.8.*:
  * monkeypatched a Dir.home method
  * fixed variable that was shadowed in 1.9, overwritten in 1.8

=== 1.0.2 / 2012-02-28

* minor enhancements:
  * change default location for "dot-" mnt directories
  * better documentation

=== 1.0.1 / 2012-02-27

* minor enhancements:
  * can place files directly in static directories now
  * cleaned up code

=== 1.0.0 / 2012-02-21

* Backwards incompatible: use Ruby for config file (not YAML)
* minor enhancements:
  * support globs or regexp for ignore_paths
  * better documentation
  * switched to bones for gem config

=== 0.9.2 / 2009-04-28

* 1 minor enhancement
  * less manual tasks required if you want to move mnts

=== 0.9.1 / 2009-04-27

* 1 minor enhancement
  * checks if pre-existing symlink points to the correct location

=== 0.9.0 / 2008-10-18

* Initial release.



